<h2>Formatting Guidelines</h2>
<ul>
  <li>Please use the <a href="http://www.ieee.org/conferences_events/conferences/publishing/templates.html">IEEE Transactions double-column format</a> with a font size of 10pt or lager.
  <li>Submissions must be in PDF format.
  <li>There is a strict limit of 10 pages.
  <li>Submissions should represent original, substantive research results.
  <li>At least one author of every accepted paper is required to attend WHIST 2011 in order for the paper to be included in the final proceedings.
  <li>Workshop proceedings will be made available on the web in electronic format.
</ul>
